Item:SXRlbTo5NDQ0NTQ=.name: Blue Buffalo Life Protection Formula Adult Beef & Brown Rice Recipe Dry Dog Food, 24-lb bag
Item:SXRlbTo5NDQ0NTQ=.description: Nourish your canine companion with a meal sure to fuel his daily adventures with Blue Buffalo LPF Beef Dog Food. Formulated to support your doggo’s overall health, this droolworthy, made-in-the-USA dry food is crafted with wholesome, natural ingredients and enhanced with a special blend of antioxidants, vitamins and minerals. Real meat is the first ingredient in this tasty, beefy recipe, and it’s also packed with real fruits, veggies and whole grains. It contains essential proteins and carbohydrates your adult dog needs, as well as omega 3 and 6 fatty acids for a beautiful coat and healthy skin. You can rest easy knowing this complete meal contains no poultry by-product meals, corn, wheat, soy or artificial flavors or preservatives.

itemSubHeader.richText: BLUE Life Protection Formula always features high-quality real meat, healthy fruits and wholesome whole grains. Like all BLUE foods, it's made from the finest natural ingredients enhanced with vitamins and minerals.

itemSubHeader.richText: BLUE has more breed size and life stage-specific foods than any other natural pet food. You'll find healthy, delicious BLUE Life Protection Formula recipes for toy, small and large breeds as well as puppies, adults and senior dogs
itemSubHeader.text: BLUE has more breed size and life stage-specific foods than any other natural pet food. You'll find healthy, delicious BLUE Life Protection Formula recipes for toy, small and large breeds as well as puppies, adults and senior dogs

header.text: The Original Healthy Formula That Started It All

itemSubHeader.richText:
BLUE is formulated with only the finest natural ingredients:

Always features protein-rich real meat

NO chicken (or poultry) by-product meals

NO corn, wheat or soy

itemHeader.text: A Sampling of Premium Natural Ingredients

header.text: A Sampling of Premium Natural Ingredients

itemSubHeader.richText: APPLES: Good source of antioxidants, vitamin A, vitamin C and dietary fiber, which promotes overall gastrointestinal health.
itemSubHeader.text: APPLES: Good source of antioxidants, vitamin A, vitamin C and dietary fiber, which promotes overall gastrointestinal health.

itemSubHeader.richText: SPINACH: Rich in carotenoids, including beta-carotene and lutein, and also contains quercetin, a phytochemical with antioxidant properties.
itemSubHeader.text: SPINACH: Rich in carotenoids, including beta-carotene and lutein, and also contains quercetin, a phytochemical with antioxidant properties.

itemSubHeader.richText: BLUEBERRIES: Loaded with vitamins C and E, healthy carbs, fiber and powerful antioxidants for immune system support and urinary tract health.
itemSubHeader.text: BLUEBERRIES: Loaded with vitamins C and E, healthy carbs, fiber and powerful antioxidants for immune system support and urinary tract health.

itemSubHeader.richText: PUMPKIN: Rich in beta-carotene, vitamin A, iron, potassium, magnesium and zinc, plus a good source of fiber to help regulate digestion.
itemSubHeader.text: PUMPKIN: Rich in beta-carotene, vitamin A, iron, potassium, magnesium and zinc, plus a good source of fiber to help regulate digestion.

header.text: A Sampling of Premium Natural Ingredients

itemSubHeader.richText: All BLUE dry food formulas feature a precise blend of vitamins, minerals and antioxidants selected by holistic veterinarians and animal nutritionists to help promote immune system health, fulfill life stage requirements and support a healthy oxidative balance.
itemSubHeader.text: All BLUE dry food formulas feature a precise blend of vitamins, minerals and antioxidants selected by holistic veterinarians and animal nutritionists to help promote immune system health, fulfill life stage requirements and support a healthy oxidative balance.

itemSubHeader.richText:
HEALTHY MUSCLE DEVELOPMENT: High-quality protein plus protein meal and egg help promote strong muscles. Small breed formulas are precisely blended to help meet small and toy breeds' higher energy needs. Large breed formulas feature L-carnitine to help promote lean muscle mass.

STRONG BONES AND TEETH: Calcium, phosphorus and essential vitamins help promote strong bones and teeth. Small breed formulas feature special "small-bite" kibble for easier chewing and tartar removal. Large breed formulas contain glucosamine and chondroitin to support joint function and mobility.

HEALTHY SKIN, COAT AND IMMUNE SYSTEM: Omega-3 and 6 fatty acids help promote a shiny coat and healthy skin. Essential vitamins, chelated minerals and important antioxidants help support the immune system.

Blue Buffalo began with unconditional love and some furry inspiration from a large breed Airedale, Blue. When Blue's family started a pet food company, their vision was clear. They wanted every pet parent to be able to feed their pet with the same care they would feed family. So they created the #1 natural pet specialty food to help furry family members live happy, healthy lives. Of course, they named it after Blue.
